### Inspect configured models
GET http://localhost:8080/api/agent/models

### Route a code fence without relying on a configured keyword
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请解释这段代码：```java\nclass Demo {}\n```"
}

